        What's Express?
        
    %p
      Looking for a fast on-ramp to the Cloud? Get Java, Ruby, PHP, Perl, and Python apps in the cloud with just a few lines of code.

    %h2
      Install
 
    %p
      Download and install the OpenShift Express client tools so you can deploy and manage your application in the cloud.  
          
    .vid  
