    %h2
      Create
   
    %p
      Create a subdomain for your application and clone the Git master repository from the cloud.
          
    .vid
      <iframe width="425" height="349" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/p83Cx6s_q1U" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
 
    %h2
      Deploy
    
    %p
      Add your application code to the Git repository and push to the cloud. Congratulations, your application is live!
    
    .vid
      <iframe width="425" height="349" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/H9rMgKCoW3w" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

  %section#videos
